---
title: Spiced Turkey with Chopped Salad and Hummus Dressing
description: This flavour-packed salad opens you up to some of our favourite Middle Eastern tastes. The warming spices mixed with juicy turkey and hearty veg will leave you feeling energized for whatever comes your way!

